2010-01-10  brettp

	* engine/lib/annotations.php: Fixes #1399: Case sensitivity was
	  never in the deprecated function, so no need to add it. Use the
	  new functions if required.
	* engine/lib/metadata.php: Fixes #538. Applied Cash's patch. This
	  is an old one...jeepers.
