	* engine/lib/tags.php: fixes #1169 as described on ticket
	* CHANGES.txt, engine/lib/api.php: updated documentation of API
	  functions - perhaps ready for developer preview
	* engine/lib/sessions.php: user object needs to be loaded from
	  database into session on each page in case the object has changed
	  - this commit also handles a user who has been deleted with an
	  active session

