2009-11-07  brettp

	* mod/search/search_hooks.php: Reverted groups and users to LIKE
	  instead of MATCH AGAINST.
	* engine/lib/group.php, engine/lib/objects.php,
	  engine/lib/tags.php, engine/lib/users.php, mod/search/index.php,
	  mod/search/search_hooks.php, mod/search/start.php,
	  mod/search/views/default/page_elements/searchbox.php,
