2009-08-28  brettp

	* actions/register.php, engine/lib/entities.php: Fixes #1196:
	  ElggEntity::disable() now accepts a 2nd arg for recursive. New
	  users are not recursively disabled for plugins that need to
	  create entities owned by the new user upon entity creation.

